How to Play
The goal is to guide Frog safely back to the pond. Plan each move carefully, avoid hazards, and try to reach the pond in the best number of moves to earn more stars.
Owls can catch Frog.
Storks fly across the board after a warning.
Rocks block movement.
Turtles and fireflies can help Frog.
Fly Feast is a fast mini-game where Frog catches flies with a stretchy tongue.
Sound and Music
Sound and music can be toggled from the in-game controls.
If you do not hear audio, check your device volume and Silent Mode settings.
Privacy
Toads Wild Adventure does not require an account, login, subscription, or purchase to play.
The app does not collect personal information, does not include user-generated content, and does not include ads.
Frequently Asked Questions
Do I need an internet connection?
No. Normal gameplay does not require an internet connection.
What is Grand Master mode?
Grand Master mode is a more challenging version of the pond puzzle game. It is designed to be harder while still remaining fair and solvable.
What is the Owl Immunity Pass?
The Owl Immunity Pass protects Frog from one owl catch in the main pond game. It can be earned through the Fly Feast mini-game.
How do streak rewards work?
Perfect 3-star levels build a streak. Reaching certain streak milestones unlocks special achievement illustrations.
